comments.text:
Refactor completed for templates.py to satisfy flake8 C901 (<=10) across targeted functions:

- TemplateConfig.validate: split into field-level helpers (_validate_grid_ranges, _validate_color_scheme, _validate_marker_config, _validate_performance_options, _strict_validation);
- RGBTemplate.validate_performance: extracted scenario loop + summarization + recs into private helpers (_rgb_collect_test_results, _rgb_performance_summary, _rgb_recommendations);
- create_custom_template: reduced to orchestration; added helpers (_validate_template_type, _validate_template_config, _instantiate_template_from_type, _initialize_or_raise);
- register_template: factored validation/initialization/smoke-test/registry entry into helpers (_assert_valid_template_name, _ensure_initialized_for_registration, _warn_on_missing_metadata, _smoke_test_template_result, _build_registry_entry);
- get_template_registry: extracted filtering/serialization into helpers (_filter_registry_items, _build_template_info) while preserving existing recommendations helper;
- optimize_template: extracted quality/caching/memory/measurement logic into helpers (_apply_quality_and_caching_optimizations, _memory_recommendations, _instantiate_and_measure_optimized);
- validate_template_performance: reduced orchestration; added helpers for target selection + benchmarks (_determine_targets_for_template, _run_benchmarks_for_template) and reused existing extracted compatibility/strict checks.

Public API remains unchanged (RGBTemplate/MatplotlibTemplate classes, factory/registry functions). Behavior and validation messages preserved where applicable. No reverse dependencies on this bead were found, so no dependent updates were required.
